ces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbig4即使係三大都一個中規中距嘅offer<br />\n大把三大bba人由officer做起，唔知捱到幾時先出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加唔好講其他major其他u</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁爸打有冇咩好建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人人唔同特點同要求<br />\n最簡單分成ibank、MT、big4<br />\n最好就梗係ibank<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就mt<br />\nMT都分大行同細行<br />\n大行mt梗係無得輸<br />\n細行mt雖然都出到2xk，但如果你想將來發展好d嘅，可能做返big4會更好<br />\n之後係big4，如果你捱得嘅，big4真心前途唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你厭audit辛苦，咪入advisory(難入)或者tax(易入)<br />\n其實政府工就再諗"},{"pid":"67a23aca4e43521e6256ac69551318d92bbe740f","tid":376450,"uid":79774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>非三大你都要勁big 4先侵你玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到好似有得你揀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\naudit黎講<br />\nPoly city的人一定多過哂3大</blockquote><br />\n係咪因爲三大啲人唔願做 先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔覺得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然poly city 係好多，但應該無三大咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbig4即使係三大都一個中規中距嘅offer<br />\n大把三大bba人由officer做起，唔知捱到幾時先出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加唔好講其他major其他u</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁爸打有冇咩好建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人人唔同特點同要求<br />\n最簡單分成ibank、MT、big4<br />\n最好就梗係ibank<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就mt<br />\nMT都分大行同細行<br />\n大行mt梗係無得輸<br />\n細行mt雖然都出到2xk，但如果你想將來發展好d嘅，可能做返big4會更好<br />\n之後係big4，如果你捱得嘅，big4真心前途唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你厭audit辛苦，咪入advisory(難入)或者tax(易入)<br />\n其實政府工就再諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來有咁多野 多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我想問advisory 係做啲咩架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋3者（audit advisory tax) 既前路如何？"},{"pid":"35c2b2ce1e481d0107bcae1f1cab67ccc367f42a","tid":376450,"uid":66500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>mt呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實mt係做啲咩 聽就有聽過 不過都係冇乜概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間間都唔同<br />\n用黎培訓未來既管理層<br />\n會輪流到唔同部門俾你做野學野<br />\n<br />\n利申:9up 都係讀緊account<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab89614070a4bdfd48821b2a8cf95df0b912e07","tid":376450,"uid":79774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>mt呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實mt係做啲咩 聽就有聽過 不過都係冇乜概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間間都唔同<br />\n用黎培訓未來既管理層<br />\n會輪流到唔同部門俾你做野學野<br />\n<br />\n利申:9up 都係讀緊account<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁巴打你有冇咩目標 或者 方向"},{"pid":"ffb3c47a72d9e23fc18f18d198eac431a271df6d","tid":376450,"uid":66500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:28:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n咁巴打你有冇咩目標 或者 方向</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最想做mt<br />\n唔得咪逼科<br />\n再唔得咪second tier<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7e12cbe12be3e8bb3c8a7886c61b17409f848a","tid":376450,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"Mt非三大已經冇乜機會<br />\n大mt e.g. Hsbc, standard chartered, swire<br />\n基本上海歸名校佔一半<br />\n三大佔另外一半<br />\n<br />\nBig 4宜家請好多city/poly <br />\n我林佔今年fg一半<br />\n<br />\nAdvisory/consulting行既路唔同<br />\n有m&amp;a advisory 有financial accounting advisory<br />\nManagement consulting/forensic<br />\n但每年只係請十幾個<br />\n唔似audit百幾二百咁請"},{"pid":"41a8650e4ffeda8a4146d96086161eae3d4f284a","tid":376450,"uid":66500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mt非三大已經冇乜機會<br />\n大mt e.g. Hsbc, standard chartered, swire<br />\n基本上海歸名校佔一半<br />\n三大佔另外一半<br />\n<br />\nBig 4宜家請好多city/poly <br />\n我林佔今年fg一半<br />\n<br />\nAdvisory/consulting行既路唔同<br />\n有m&amp;a advisory 有financial accounting advisory<br />\nManagement consulting/forensic<br />\n但每年只係請十幾個<br />\n唔似audit百幾二百咁請</blockquote><br />\nmt有冇話gpa最低幾多<br />\n僅僅過3係咪冇機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaebcb215011c6b09be0ba5e148dcd13708f8c7","tid":376450,"uid":9729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"MT狂熱之下好多細公司都用MT呢個名請打雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBig4 Advisory唔識人真係唔洗諗<br />\n<br />\nAudit其實請好多非三大既人<br />\n你話Audit既人係唔係好醒<br />\n講真 醒點同iBank Corp Fin果D比<br />\n自己先天不足咪用後天努力彌補<br />\n算唔上搵到咩大錢 但真係唔洗太憂生活囉"},{"pid":"159f4f99de3aa9647aecba4880764ab62bf5359f","tid":376450,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mt非三大已經冇乜機會<br />\n大mt e.g. Hsbc, standard chartered, swire<br />\n基本上海歸名校佔一半<br />\n三大佔另外一半<br />\n<br />\nBig 4宜家請好多city/poly <br />\n我林佔今年fg一半<br />\n<br />\nAdvisory/consulting行既路唔同<br />\n有m&amp;a advisory 有financial accounting advisory<br />\nManagement consulting/forensic<br />\n但每年只係請十幾個<br />\n唔似audit百幾二百咁請</blockquote><br />\ncity poly佔一半又無可能<br />\n你話佢地同三大一比一我都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有一大班海歸同非五大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a6d38eccf8521782bbf3fae7783b5544f03af3","tid":376450,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>MT狂熱之下好多細公司都用MT呢個名請打雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBig4 Advisory唔識人真係唔洗諗<br />\n<br />\nAudit其實請好多非三大既人<br />\n你話Audit既人係唔係好醒<br />\n講真 醒點同iBank Corp Fin果D比<br />\n自己先天不足咪用後天努力彌補<br />\n算唔上搵到咩大錢 但真係唔洗太憂生活囉</blockquote><br />\nadvisory又唔係難到咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多唔識人都收到啦<br />\n始終個起薪同audit一樣低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而佢前景就真係好睇個人"},{"pid":"22303a68ec55d8c7662f43d3dcd97be348355815","tid":376450,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:11:49.000Z","msg":"會計grad 四大有三間offer 依做緊銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0735a5bc948461473c00ca52e11069e37d800dd","tid":376450,"uid":140546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:13:14.000Z","msg":"做左1年local firm都唔知做緊咩，都好迷茫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b0eeb6e0e8f6ff4f7efbc018b40bd6e7075c39","tid":376450,"uid":79774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>MT狂熱之下好多細公司都用MT呢個名請打雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBig4 Advisory唔識人真係唔洗諗<br />\n<br />\nAudit其實請好多非三大既人<br />\n你話Audit既人係唔係好醒<br />\n講真 醒點同iBank Corp Fin果D比<br />\n自己先天不足咪用後天努力彌補<br />\n算唔上搵到咩大錢 但真係唔洗太憂生活囉</blockquote><br />\nadvisory又唔係難到咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多唔識人都收到啦<br />\n始終個